<header class="page-header"><div class="container">
  <h1>Your Complete Weight Loss Product 减脂产品</h1>
  <p>Science-based nutrition, exercise, and lifestyle guidance to support your product journey. All free.</p>
</div></header>

<section class="section" style="background:var(--white);padding:1.5rem 0;"><div class="container text-center"><p style="font-size:.95rem;color:var(--light);max-width:650px;margin:0 auto;">Choosing to use a weight loss product is a personal decision. There is no shame in getting support for your health goals. You are not taking shortcuts - you are taking care of yourself. ❤️</p></div></section><!-- Quick Nav --><div style="background:#fff3cd;border:1px solid #ffc107;padding:1rem;border-radius:8px;margin:2rem auto;max-width:800px;font-size:.85rem;"><strong>Important:</strong> This content is for educational purposes only. It does not constitute medical advice. Always consult your healthcare provider before starting, changing, or stopping any product or treatment plan. FitHer does not endorse, prescribe, or sell any products.</div>
